These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, prince, game, bolivar
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, bridge, go
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, azalea, amaryllis
House: cape-cod, futuristic, modern, art-deco
1. the person playing whist is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person playing canasta##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person playing whist is the cape-cod house##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the modern house##1
9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | swisher  | bolivar  | prince | game |
| Game           | whist | canasta | go  | bridge  |
| Flower   | amaryllis       | azalea      | iris | aconite      |
| House           | cape-cod          | futuristic     | modern    | art-deco     |

