.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, iris, daisy
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, security-guard, musician, doctor
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, camping, gardening
House: art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman, palace
1. the chef is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the art-deco house##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the security-guard##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
9. the art-deco house is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Flower      | iris     | daffodil       | poppy | daisy        |
| Job          | doctor     | security-guard       | musician   | chef   |
| Hobby   | camping      | photography       | gardening     | card-games    |
| House         | craftsman | palace | art-deco | ranch-style |

