.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, july, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, skiing, badminton
4 different games are played: poker, chess, billiard, bridge
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bluemaster, cain, dannemann
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday      | april | august       | november        | july        |
| Sport           | volleyball   | skiing | surfing   | badminton |
| Game   | poker     | chess    | bridge | billiard        |
| Cigar           | cain         | vegafina  | dannemann       | bluemaster         |

