3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food           | cranberry   | raspberry  | cucumber | lemon |
