.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
City: hamburg, prague, london, rome
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, tram, bike
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, art-deco, cottage
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, zucchini, peas, potato
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
2. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the person eating potato##1
6. the person eating potato is the art-deco house##1
7. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| City           | hamburg  | london    | prague | rome |
| Transport   | tram      | skateboard    | ship         | bike    |
| House   | gothic-revival   | craftsman     | art-deco          | cottage      |
| Food         | zucchini | blueberry | potato      | peas      |

