 5. the person who likes white is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 9. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
10. the modern house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | juice  | sprite | coffee     | hot-chocolate |
| Flower           | lily  | amaryllis      | azalea | begonia    |
