 8. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
